    title: 'Do chronic respiratory diseases or their treatment affect the risk of SARS-CoV-2 infection?',
    summary: 'Do chronic respiratory diseases or their treatment affect the risk of SARS-CoV-2 infection?',
    fundingStatement: 'None',
