    copyrightLicence: 'CC-BY',
    carriedOut: false,
    text: '<p><strong>Do&nbsp;chronic&nbsp;respiratory&nbsp;diseases&nbsp;or their treatment&nbsp;affect the&nbsp;risk&nbsp;of SARS-CoV-2 infection?</strong></p><p>Coronavirus&nbsp;disease 2019 (COVID-19), caused by&nbsp;the novel severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), is an acute respiratory&nbsp;disease&nbsp;that can lead&nbsp;to respiratory failure and&nbsp;death.&nbsp;Previous epidemics&nbsp;of novel coronavirus&nbsp;diseases,&nbsp;such as severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS)&nbsp;and Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS),&nbsp;were&nbsp;associated&nbsp;with similar clinical features and&nbsp;outcomes.&nbsp;One might anticipate&nbsp;that patients&nbsp;with chronic&nbsp;respiratory diseases,&nbsp;particularly&nbsp;chronic obstructive&nbsp;pulmonary&nbsp;disease (COPD) and asthma,&nbsp;would be at&nbsp;increased risk&nbsp;of SARS-CoV-2 infection and more severe&nbsp;presentations&nbsp;of&nbsp;COVID-19.</p><title>tmp/ayne0tfnyu1yvbusddnnm-html.html</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"><style type="text/css">p{margin:0;padding:0}.ft20{font-size:16px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft21{font-size:8px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft22{font-size:8px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft23{font-size:8px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft24{font-size:13px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft25{font-size:5px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft26{font-size:13px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft27{font-size:10px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft28{font-size:13px;line-height:19px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft29{font-size:13px;line-height:23px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft210{font-size:8px;line-height:13px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft211{font-size:8px;line-height:18px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft212{font-size:13px;line-height:18px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft213{font-size:10px;line-height:21px;font-family:Times;color:#000}</style><div id="page2-div" style="position:relative;width:892px;height:1199px"><br><p style="position:absolute;top:968px;left:538px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft22">.</p></div><style type="text/css">p{margin:0;padding:0}.ft10{font-size:25px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft11{font-size:8px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft12{font-size:8px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft13{font-size:8px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft14{font-size:13px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft15{font-size:5px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft16{font-size:7px;font-family:Times;color:#00539e}.ft17{font-size:7px;font-family:Times;color:#00539e}.ft18{font-size:7px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft19{font-size:7px;font-family:Times;color:#4e6a74}.ft110{font-size:3px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft111{font-size:8px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft112{font-size:7px;font-family:Times;color:#4e6a74}.ft113{font-size:25px;line-height:34px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft114{font-size:13px;line-height:19px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft115{font-size:7px;line-height:17px;font-family:Times;color:#00539e}.ft116{font-size:7px;line-height:13px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft117{font-size:8px;line-height:16px;font-family:Times;color:#000}.ft118{font-size:7px;line-height:12px;font-family:Times;color:#000}</style>',
